race.comment: Open race to close out the card. SUPER TWENTY THREE (2) is yet to miss a drum in five attempts over this track and trip and has a good affiliation with gun hoop Wiggins who has three wins and six placings from 14 rides. Will be cherry-ripe for this contest and should be right there when the whips are cracking. PONTIUS (9) was in the betting when facing the starter for the first time and didn't let backers down with a solid win around this circuit. Looks to have plenty of upside and can go right on with the job now. LOOMING ONE (1) returned in good order with a solid Cairns victory and winning rider Holt stays in the stirrups. Expected to feature in the finish again. HELL OF A BENTLEY (8) strips fitter third-up from the spell and gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim. Solid top-three prospect. DALT JAZ (3) rounds out the selections.
